text: Þis syndan þæs wudes gemeara in to Readanoran, i pirit.
Andlang englungadene eal swa wæterwile yruan innan þæne hæþenan byrgels.
Of þan hæðenan byrgels be wyrtwalan innan baruot sæd.
And of barfot sæde innan timbersæd, & of timbersæde innan steapan cnolles scyd.
And of steapan cnolles scydde on hanslædes hæfdan, & of hanslædes heafdan innan grenan weg.
And of þam grenan wege innan healdæ mæres hling, & of þam hlince innan stanoranlege.
And of stanoran lege innan stanmeres hling, & of stanmeres hlince on cadendtes heafdan.
And of cadenes heafdan on holemeres hling, & of holemeres hling innan stanbeorh.
And of stan beorhge innan þæne smalan ærc, of þon smalan ærc sce innan þone mapeldre on west halfe asumedcre.
Of þan mapeldre <ine> <es> wyrte pitte innan dragemeres hling.
And of dragemeres hlince innan ruganwic, & of ruganwic innan depan hauisteal on hremryrc.
And of hremhrycce on þere fulan slostendan mapeldere ofer innan sigerdene.
And of sigerdene innan badandene on clacces wadland, & of clacces wadlande into lufemere, lufanmere, þær ut on þæne feld.
